rule.gray_area:
"As a rule" signals this is strong guidance, not absolute law. Context and genre
determine how strictly to apply. Academic prose benefits from explicit topic sentences;
creative prose may achieve effects through less obvious organization.

when_purpose_requires_deviation.resolution:
If unconventional structure creates emphasis or rhythm that serves communicative
purpose, and reader won't mistake it for error, use it. But use sparingly;
constant rule-breaking becomes formlessness.
